extends layout

block title
  | Welcome to PopIt

block content

  div#promo-box
    h1 Welcome to PopIt
    
    p
      | PopIt makes it simple to start and maintain a public database of 
      | people, organisations and positions.
    
    p
      | Create your own site and you can start to enter details 
      | and share them with others as web pages or over an API. You can store 
      | contact details and links to other sites, and photos.
  
    p
      a(href='/instances/new', class='btn') Create your PopIt site
  
    p
      a(href='/instances', class='btn') Browse existing sites
